quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,99,"kma qasasna ealayk - 'ayuha alrasul - 'anba' musaa wafireawn wqwmhma, nkhbrk banba' alssabiqin lk. waqad ataynak min eindina hdha alquran dhikraa liman ytdhkr"
  20,100,"mn 'aerid ean hdha alqran, walam yusadiq bh, walam yaemal bima fyh, fa'iinah yati rabih yawm alqiamat yahmil 'ithmana ezymana"
  20,101,"khaldyn fi aledhab, wsa'hm dhlk alhml althaqil min alatham hayth awrdhm alnar"
  20,102,"ywm yanfukh almlak fi \"alqrn\" lsyht albeth, wanasuq alkafirin dhlkm alyawm wahum zrq, tghyart alwanhm weywnhm; min shdt al'ahdath walahwal"
  20,103,"ythamswn bynhm, yaqul bedhm lbed: ma labithtum fi alhayat aldunya 'iilaa eshrt ayam"
  20,104,nahn 'aelam bima yaqulun wyusirrun hyn yaqul aelmhm wawfahm eqla ma labithtum 'iilaa ywmana wahdana; lqisar mdt aldunya fi 'anfusihim yawm alqyamt
  20,105,"wysalk - 'ayuha alrasul - qawmak ean masir aljibal yawm alqyamt, faqul lhm: yzylha rbbi ean amaknha fyjelha haba'an mnbthana"
  20,106,"fytrk al'ard hinayidh mnbstt mstwyt mlsa' la naba'at fyha, la yaraa alnazr 'iilayha min astwayha mayla wala artfaeana wala ankhfadana"
  20,107,"fytrk al'ard hinayidh mnbstt mstwyt mlsa' la naba'at fyha, la yaraa alnazr 'iilayha min astwayha mayla wala artfaeana wala ankhfadana"
  20,108,"fy dhlk alyawm yatabie alnaas sawt aldaaei 'iilaa mawqif alqyamt, la mhyd ean daewatan aldaey; li'anaha haqa wasadaq lajamie alkhlq, wsknt al'aswat khdweana llrhmn, fala tasmae minha 'iilaa swtana khfyana"
  20,109,"fy dhlk alyawm laa tanfae alshafaeat ahdana min alkhlq, 'illa 'iidha 'adhin alrhmn llshafe, waradi ean almshfwe lh, wala yakun dhalik 'iilaa lilmuaman almkhls"
  20,110,"yelm allah ma bayn 'aydi alnaas min 'amr alqiamat wama khalfahum min 'amr aldnya, wala yhyt khalaqah bih elmana subhanah wteala"
  20,111,"wkhdet wujuh alkhlayq, wdhllat lkhalqha, aladhi lah jmye maeani alhayat alkamilat kama ylyq bjlalh aldhy la ymwt, alqayim ealaa tadbir kll shy', almstghny emman swah. waqad khasir yawm alqiamat man 'ushrik mae allah ahdana min khlqh"
  20,112,"wmn yaemal salhat al'aemal wahu mumin brbh, fala yakhaf zlmana biziadat syyath, wala hdmana bnqs hsnath"
  20,113,"wkma rghghabna 'ahl al'iiman fi salhat alaemal, whdhdharna 'ahl alkufr min almaqam ealaa measyhm wakufrihim bayatna, 'anzalna hdha alquran ballsan alerby; lyfhmwh, wfssalna fih anwaeana min alweyd; raja' 'ana ytqu rbhm, 'aw yuhdith lahum hdha alquran tdhkrt, fytezu, wyetbru"